title: Complete Hellsing Manga
description:
This is just trollet-ost's Hellsing torrent but updated with the last few chapters up to the end of the manga.

Includes: All 95 chapters of the main hellsing manga, all 6 released chapters of the Hellsing: The Dawn prequel series and some random extras.

All in .cbz format so you'll need to get cdisplay if you haven't already.

I'm not too sure about the chapter listings for volume 9, so I've just put all the chapters from 87-95 as volume 9, if it's meant to be volume 10, sorry. You can rearrange them yourself by changing the format back into regular .zip and then moving the files around.
